Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.46,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}You're My Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.87,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}ココロを開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:06.72,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(100,100)\an9}打ち明けたいゆずれない想いを
